OL,5, Conspiracy theorist Alex Jones has     
OL,6, filed for personal bankruptcy after he 
OL,7, was ordered to pay almost $1.5bn       
OL,8, (#1.2bn) for falsely claiming a 2012   
OL,9, school shooting was a hoax.            
OL,11,FJones was ordered to pay the damages to
OL,12,Fthe families of the victims of the     
OL,13,FSandy Hook shooting following a series 
OL,14,Fof defamation trials earlier this year.
OL,16,FThe most notable came in October when a
OL,17,Fjury ordered him to pay almost $1bn    
OL,18,Ffollowing a trial in Connecticut.      
OL,20,FJones has not commented on the filing. 
